# grapher_trace_domain_smoke.numos — Phase 10D. Trace robustness across domain
# holes: f0 tan(x) (asymptotes), f1 ln(x) (undefined for x<=0). Traces tan near
# the origin, switches to ln and traces into x<0. Proves the trace readout shows
# "y=--- (off domain)" instead of a literal "nan" when the function is undefined,
# and that asymptotes no longer smear as solid vertical lines. Warning-only.
log "trace domain: start"
wait 200
open_app Grapher
wait 60
key down
key enter
key tan
key x
key right
key enter
wait 30
key down
key enter
key ln
key x
key right
key enter
wait 60
key graph
wait 60
key enter
wait 20
key left
key left
key left
wait 20
screenshot out/grapher_trace_domain_tan.ppm
key up
wait 20
key left
key left
key left
key left
key left
key left
wait 20
screenshot out/grapher_trace_domain_ln.ppm
assert_app Grapher
log "trace domain: off-domain handled"
